name: Huge Brooklyn Brownstone Living, Close to it all.
transit: This is a great location for every type of public transportation. Steps outside my building is the bus heading to Williamsburg, only a 3 min walk of 2 blocks is the train which runs 24 hours a day each day and connects you to Manhattan within 25 mins. We are also a great destination for cabs both private and public car services. This location is also a fun area to walk around and check out the bars, cafes and restaurants tucked in every little nook.
